      document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function(){
          window.nrVideoTrackerCreated = false; // tracking this to prevent duplicates, just in case the creation process takes longer than the next loop
          var getVideoId = setInterval(function(){  // it takes a while for legacy info to come to NG and get the video wrapper class
            if (typeof nrvideo !== 'undefined') {  // check to make sure the nrvideo library is loaded
              if (   typeof wnVideoWidgets !== 'undefined'
                  && typeof wnVideoWidgets.canvasObject !== 'undefined'
                  && typeof Object.keys(wnVideoWidgets.canvasObject) !== 'undefined'
                  && typeof Object.keys(wnVideoWidgets.canvasObject)[0] !== 'undefined'
                  && typeof wnVideoWidgets.canvasObject[Object.keys(wnVideoWidgets.canvasObject)[0]] !== 'undefined') {  // check for existence of our video variable(s)

                  var vidKey = Object.keys(wnVideoWidgets.canvasObject)[0];
                  var vidValue = wnVideoWidgets.canvasObject[Object.keys(wnVideoWidgets.canvasObject)[0]];

                  if (typeof pageWidgets[vidKey][vidValue] !== 'undefined' && typeof pageWidgets[vidKey][vidValue].htmlVersion !== 'undefined' && typeof pageWidgets[vidKey][vidValue].htmlVersion.canvas !== 'undefined') {
                    var player = pageWidgets[vidKey][vidValue].htmlVersion.canvas;

                    if (typeof window.nrVideoTracker === 'undefined' && !window.nrVideoTrackerCreated) {  // start the tracker if we don't have one already. don't wait for customData
                      window.nrVideoTrackerCreated = true;
                      if (pageWidgets[vidKey][vidValue].htmlVersion.constructor.name === "FranklyVJSVideoCanvas") {
                        // console.log("*** Starting VideoJS nrVideoTracker");
                        window.nrVideoTracker = new nrvideo.VideojsTracker(player);
                      } else {
                        // console.log("*** Starting AMP nrVideoTracker");
                        window.nrVideoTracker = new nrvideo.AmpTracker(player);
                      }
                      nrvideo.Core.addTracker(window.nrVideoTracker);                
                    }
                    
                    if (typeof pageWidgets[vidKey][vidValue].clipObj !== 'undefined') {
                      var currentClip = pageWidgets[vidKey][vidValue].clipObj;

                      if (typeof currentClip.headline !== 'undefined' && typeof currentClip.affiliateName !== 'undefined' && typeof currentClip.id !== 'undefined' ) {
                        if (typeof window.nrVideoTracker !== 'undefined') {
                          window.nrVideoTracker.customData = {
                              contentTitle: currentClip.headline,
                              domain: window.location.hostname,
                              affiliateName: currentClip.affiliateName,
                              clipId: currentClip.id
                          };
                          stopGetId(); // stop looking for the video wrapper
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
              }

            }
          }, 50);
          function stopGetId() {
            clearInterval(getVideoId);
            clearTimeout(getVideoTimeout);
          }
          var getVideoTimeout = setTimeout(function(){
            stopGetId()
          }, 30000);
      });
